\begin_layout Section*
Market positioning or internal resources for competitiveness?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We will investigate the factors that affect the competetivness of EA DICE,
 and apply theories and concepts from operations management to relevant
 conditions concerning these two companies.
 Since strategic market decisions are made by EA, and operative decisions
 are made at DICE, certain concepts may only apply accordingly.
